songs.title: Extra
songs.lyrics:
[Chorus]
I’m rollin’ up that extendo, I’m extra
I’m pullin’ up to the club, I’m leavin’ with all of the bitches, I’m extra
I’m ridin’ ‘round with the narcotics, I’m extra
I’m ridin’ ‘round, sippin’ that mud, I’m extra

[Verse]
I bought an extra clip for my toolie for niggas on extra shit
I had to kick out my ex-bitch extra quick ‘cause she was on extra shit
Congratulated, my coupe goes so fast, my horses, they be on that extra shit
Bitch, I got extra cups and extra medicine, bitch, I got extra bullets in the cabinets
Roll the extra dope I’m bringin’ it, brand new drop top, I’ma get it
All these tats, no extra pigment, all these racks is extra bitches
Bitches want a kiss, they must be extra kiddin’, new coupe and it’s extra kitted
Smokin’ in the cup and it’s extra tinted, spinnin’ out, the extra ignant
Got them creepin’, lookin’ for some extra bitches, hit the corner, I just seen an extra thick one
My bankroll an extra big one, hit the stove, four watches, bought an extra sick one
Switchin’ lanes too fast, I need an extra signal, pouring’ extra mud, my cup stay extra filthy
Flipped to buy a extra building, my bitch in her extra feelings
Conversation with a millionaire, I just brainstorm on how the fuck to get one
Walked in Diesel for some underwear, be payin’ extra, you know I can’t pick one
My two-door extra slippery, my new whore extra fit one
Jackie Chan, you chop a brick to get paid, you be extra drug dealin’
Killin’ shit, I’m extra guilty, extra mud got me feelin’ extra tilted
I sip extra lean, I shoot extra bullets, until it is extra empty
What the fuck you mean? I travel with Nadine in case she want a extra bullet
I got extra bullets that don’t need an extra reason to get on the bullshit, yeah

[Chorus]
I’m rollin’ up that extendo, I’m extra
I’m pullin’ up to the club, I’m leavin’ with all of the bitches, I’m extra
I’m ridin’ ‘round with the narcotics, I’m extra
I’m ridin’ ‘round, sippin’ that mud, I’m extra
